flowRoot.flowPara: 1) To set flag color, set flag.panel.fill = #hex_color
2) To set error color, set error.cross.fill = #hex_color
3) To set hint color, set hint.checkmark.fill = #hex_color
4) To set question mark color, set #questionMarkGlyph.fill = #hex_color

4) To set cell colors, set #cell_up_color and #cell_down_color to the *same* #hexcolor. Gradients/opacity in tiles do the tinting. This way, we can have oddly shaped kminefields in the future, and the borders and the background outside the minefield can be easily set.
5) To set a number color, set #arabic[One | Two | n | Seven| Eight]Glyph.fill = #hex_color
6) To set the main widget background, set #backgroundPanel = #hex_color
7) #reload icon can be used *instead* of smileys.
